A pgas consumer scaffolded by [`claude-pgas-plugin`](https://github.com/simodelne/claude-pgas-plugin) v0.2.

**Engine pin:** `@simodelne/pgas-*@{{ENGINE_VERSION}}`
**Status:** Phase 0 (scaffold) — write your first program under `programs/`.

## Quick start

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies (requires NPM_TOKEN with read:packages on simodelne)
export NPM_TOKEN=ghp_...
npm install

# 2. Copy and fill in env vars
cp .env.example .env.local
$EDITOR .env.local

# 3. Install pre-commit hooks
bash scripts/install-hooks.sh

# 4. Run
npm run dev
```

